<H3> <TI>   Kovac, Moravcik Walk Out of Government Session </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1502102794 Bratislava Rozhlasova Stanica Slovensko Network 
in Slovak 0900 GMT 15 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1502102794 </F>
<F P=104>  Bratislava Rozhlasova Stanica Slovensko Network 
