<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105>Slovak </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpts] Privatization projects are the main point on the 
agenda of today's deliberations of the Slovak Government in 
Bratislava. [passage omitted] Five minutes into the meeting, 
