<H3> <TI>   Maltese President Arrives on Official Visit </TI></H3>
<H4>   Tabone Ends Visit, Departs </H4>
<F P=102> AU1002192694 Tirana ATA in English 0908 GMT 10 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> AU1002192694 </F>
<F P=104>  Tirana ATA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Tirana, February 10 (ATA) -- President of Malta Dr. 
Censu Tabone completed his official visit in Albania on February 
9. Dr. Tabone came to Albania at the invitation of President of 
Albania Sali Berisha. 
  During his four day visit in Albania, President Tabone met 
with senior Albanian officials including President Berisha, 
Premier Aleksander Meksi and the Speaker of the parliament 
Pjeter Arbnori. The talks focused on the concretization of the 
relations between the two countries. 

</TEXT>

