Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Warsaw, Feb. 14 -- According to chairman of the NATO 
Military Committee, Marshal Richard Vincent, all NATO commanders 
are strong supporters of Poland's admission to the organization, 
spokesman for the College of Polish Armed Forces Commanders, 
Major Mariusz Jedrzejko, said on Monday [14 February] after the 
meeting between Vincent and the chief of the General Staff, 
General Tadeusz Wilecki. 
  Marshal Vincent, who is paying a two-day visit to Poland, 
