of the Sejm Defence Committee Jerzy Szmajdzinski on Monday. His 
talks with Szmajdzinski focused primarily on "Partnership for 
Peace." Szmajdzinski said after the meeting that NATO wants 
serious attention to be paid to this initiative and proposes 
working out a new and detailed plan for further mutual contacts. 
  On Tuesday [15 February] Richard Vincent will meet with 
ministers of defence Piotr Kolodziejczyk and foreign affairs 
Andrzej Olechowski. 

