<H4>   Peace Process Discussed </H4>
<F P=102> AU1502110894 Bucharest ROMPRES in English 0942 GMT 15 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> AU1502110894 </F>
<F P=104>  Bucharest ROMPRES </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Bucharest, ROMPRES, 15/02/1994 -- Croatian 
President Franjo Tudjman, now visiting Romania, had an interview 
at the Chamber of Deputies headquarters with the parliament's 
president and speaker, Oliviu Gherman and Adrian Nastase, on 
February 15 morning. 
  They exchanged information and views on the organization and 
functioning of the legislative institutions in the two countries. 
  Romanian parliamentary representatives offered the Romanian 
