Croatian president showed interest in the Romanian offer. 
  The interview was attended by Ioan Lup, vice-president of 
the 
Senate, and Ion Ratiu, deputy speaker of the Chamber of Deputies. 
  President Tudjman will meet today also with Romanian Prime 
Minister Nicolae Vacaroiu, will take a short trip to the Prahova 
Valley, and meet with representatives with the Croatian minority 
of Romania later in the evening. 

