<F P=100> ROMANIA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Farmers Union Begins Warning Strike </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  AU1602132494 Bucharest Radio Romania Network in Romanian 
1100 GMT 16 Feb 94 </F>

<F P=103> AU1602132494 </F>
<F P=104>  Bucharest Radio Romania Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Romanian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Approximately 300 trade unions affiliated to the 
Agrostar Trade Union Federation, which represent the interests 
of workers in the state agricultural sectors, organized a 
two-hour warning strike this morning. During this time, work 
came to a complete standstill. This warning strike is the 
beginning of large-scale labor actions due to a labor conflict 
between the executive and the Agrostar Free Trade Union 
Federation, our reporter Marin Eftimie informs us. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

